org.sd.nlp
Class LexicalEntry

java.lang.Object
  org.sd.nlp.LexicalEntry

public class LexicalEntry
extends java.lang.Object

A lexical entry holds a lexical tokenizer pointer that includes a string with its categories (definition), if any.

Author:
Spence Koehler
